{"tid":2174704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正視黃圈衰落現況 以「要」代「屌」","createTime":"2020-08-26T05:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T05:34:04.000Z","uid":336040,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be4540c7230c226a6e628f6857706bebc1208bc9","tid":2174704,"uid":336040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:03:22.000Z","msg":"香港人，唔好再被帶風向了<br />\n清算、對真相尋根究底係好重要<br />\n但望住一日比一日荒謬嘅新聞講句「屌」畀個嬲嬲，呢種廉價義怒係無生產力的（至少可以保持熱度）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/utzsP8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FutzsP8o.png&h=b0297c0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"large\">唔好再畀政權屌打，一齊主動岀擊說「要」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>一直都有一樣更重要嘅事，係和勇絕對可以一齊做的：<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">「#要撐良心小店 #要撐黃圈」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要救黃圈，<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>#電子預售券 </strong></span></span>呢個模式真係要大大力推<br />\n連紅資老麥都搵陳奕迅日9日賣廣告推電子券<br />\n你就知係現今疫情下嘅岀路<br />\n知香港人好L有錢，但同時都知香港人好L懶，好鐘意飯來張口（包括我自己）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3thsVg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3thsVg.jpg&h=f363140d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個叫HoKoGuide香港街嘅電子券平台<br />\n開咗差不多成年，但好少人識，今日喺蘋果落全版廣告<br />\n電子券原理係<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"large\">「先課金，後享用」</span></span><br />\n解決小店欠缺現金流嘅問題<br />\n優點：<br />\n1. 有個網頁集合晒多區良心小店<br />\n2. 疫情下岀唔到街都可以支持小店<br />\n3. 仲可以買完send條link就請到朋友/手足食飯<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1. 唔係App，只提供link<br />\n2. 唔夠多小店加盟<br />\n（黃boss想加盟可click呢度：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3hvrQRo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3hvrQRo&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=c36425b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3hvrQRo</a>）<br />\n3. 付款得PayPal<br />\n<br />\n希望推到人人都識，相信連登力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>HoKoGuide香港街</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hokoguide/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhokoguide%2F&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDjIStCm0mHK7%2Bbmf%2BnNiY0c%3D&h=7cc86d3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hokoguide/</a> <br />\n唔好灰心，持續撐同路人！"},{"pid":"973ea27483d77be6ac9337e37e58a862ceccfa50","tid":2174704,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:05:03.000Z","msg":"推!!"},{"pid":"cec2ba2b2c747973e643d9e9f5faf575cbffcda6","tid":2174704,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:05:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a91cb775e36edc90c081dc7b85c0641b024828de","tid":2174704,"uid":192735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:06:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4263c1892915169ba4b109ea4d6b625c722b8592","tid":2174704,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91125bd554790f2da24fc02fd820f59c2c0d7cbd","tid":2174704,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"511b2fa9714b1eb578b26e2ffc5e4b4598364779","tid":2174704,"uid":53675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T05:34:04.000Z","msg":"有用PO 推！"}]}